docs.abstract: With universities, an international airport and lots of space, the New Jersey city says it is the perfect location for the online retailer’s second headquarters.

docs.lead_paragraph: The city sits astride an extensive transportation network of trains, planes and automobiles. It has six colleges and universities with a total of 60,000 students. docs.abstract: Machines will make a raft of decisions for my kids and others like them as they proceed through life. I’m worried.
docs.snippet: Machines will make a raft of decisions for my kids and others like them as they proceed through life. I’m worried.
docs.lead_paragraph: “You are going to have a chance to play with Alexa,” I told my daughter, Grace, who’s 3 years old. Pointing at the black cylindrical device, I explained that the speaker, also known as the Amazon Echo, was a bit like Siri but smarter. “You can ask it anything you want,” I said nonchalantly.
